# Top-level dev/tooling dependencies. Source of truth.
# Generate the locked requirements-dev.txt with hashes:
#
#     pip-compile --generate-hashes --output-file=requirements-dev.txt requirements-dev.in
#
# Do NOT edit requirements-dev.txt by hand.

# Constrain to the runtime lock so dev tools don't pull conflicting versions.
-c requirements.txt

